OL,3,CLetby attacks could have been spotted
OL,4,Cearlier if 'dots joined up' ` Jeremy
OL,5,CHunt
OL,7,FThe attack spree of killer nurse Lucy
OL,8,FLetby could have been spotted earlier
OL,9,Fwith the "dots joined up" by an
OL,10,Findependent medical examiner, former
OL,11,FHealth Secretary Jeremy Hunt has told
OL,12,Fa public inquiry.
OL,14,FGiving evidence at the Thirlwall
OL,15,FInquiry into Letby's crimes, the
OL,16,FConservative MP apologised to the
OL,17,Ffamilies of her victims as he
OL,18,Facknowledged the "appalling crime"
OL,19,Ftook place under his watch and he bore
OL,20,Fultimate responsibility for the NHS.
