OL,3,CLetby attacks could have been spotted
OL,4,Cearlier if 'dots joined up' ` Jeremy
OL,5,CHunt
OL,7,FLetby, 35, murdered seven babies and
OL,8,Fattempted to murder seven more between
OL,9,FJune 2015 and June 2016 while she
OL,10,Fworked as a nurse on the neonatal unit
OL,11,Fat the Countess of Chester Hospital.
OL,13,FThe introduction of medical examiners
OL,14,Facross the NHS in England and Wales to
OL,15,Fprovide independent scrutiny of causes
OL,16,Fof death, address any concerns from
OL,17,Fbereaved families, work with coroners
OL,18,Fand review medical records had been
OL,19,Frecommended by previous healthcare
OL,20,Finquiries.
