OL,5,CHunt
OL,7,FThe system was first suggested by the
OL,8,Finquiry into the crimes of serial
OL,9,Fkiller GP Harold Shipman in 2004 and
OL,10,Fthen further recommended by Sir Robert
OL,11,FFrancis in his 2013 report into the
OL,12,Fneglect of hundreds of patients at Mid
OL,13,FStaffordshire NHS Foundation Trust,
OL,14,Fthe inquiry heard.
OL,16,FMr Hunt said it was only when the
OL,17,Fissue of funding medical examiners
OL,18,Fcame across his desk again in 2023
OL,19,Fwhen he was chancellor that he "pushed
OL,20,Fit through".
