OL,7,FSince last September all deaths in any
OL,8,Fhealth setting in England and Wales
OL,9,Fthat are not investigated by a coroner
OL,10,Fare being reviewed by NHS medical
OL,11,Fexaminers.
OL,13,FMr Hunt said: "This terrible tragedy
OL,14,Fhappened on my watch and although I
OL,15,Fdon't bear direct personal
OL,16,Fresponsibility for everything that
OL,17,Fhappens in every ward in the NHS, you
OL,18,Fdo have ultimate responsibility for
OL,19,Fthe NHS.
OL,26,@uD@OOU
