OL,3,CLetby attacks could have been spotted
OL,4,Cearlier if 'dots joined up' ` Jeremy
OL,5,CHunt
OL,7,F"And insofar as lessons were not
OL,8,Flearned from previous inquiries that
OL,9,Fcould have been, or the right systems
OL,10,Fwere not in place that could have
OL,11,Fprevented this appalling tragedy, then
OL,12,FI do bear ultimate responsibility and
OL,13,FI want to put on the record my
OL,14,Fapologies to the families for anything
OL,15,Fthat did not happen that potentially
OL,16,Fcould have prevented such an appalling
OL,17,Fcrime.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
