OL,3,CLetby attacks could have been spotted
OL,4,Cearlier if 'dots joined up' ` Jeremy
OL,5,CHunt
OL,7,F"I think one of the things that could
OL,8,Fhave potentially meant that what
OL,9,Fhappened at the Countess of Chester
OL,10,Fwas spotted earlier and the dots were
OL,11,Fjoined up would have been having
OL,12,Fmedical examiners."
OL,14,FHe suggested medical examiners should
OL,15,Fbe trained to see the signs or
OL,16,Fpatterns of malicious harm in the work
OL,17,Fof a healthcare professional and that
OL,18,Fhaving "malicious actors" such as
OL,19,FShipman and Letby at the backs of
OL,20,Ftheir minds could make a "big
OL,21,Fdifference".
