OL,5,CHunt
OL,7,FThe inquiry heard that a non-statutory
OL,8,Frollout of medical examiners in
OL,9,FEngland and Wales began in 2019.
OL,11,FMr Hunt said: "I think the medical
OL,12,Fexaminer system when it works well is
OL,13,Fincredibly important to a healthcare
OL,14,Fsystem because I think it's not just
OL,15,Fimportant for learning from mistakes,
OL,16,Fit's also very important for families
OL,17,Fwho have been bereaved to have someone
OL,18,Findependent that they can talk to and
OL,19,Fraise concerns.
